# UPI-Fraud-Detection-Project
**My First Ever Data Science Capstone Project**

| Day | Phase | Tasks | Deliverables |
|-----|-------|-------|--------------|
| 1 | Data Understanding & Exploration | Upload dataset, explore (`head()`, `info()`, `describe()`), check missing values, basic line plots | `DAY_1_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 2 | Data Understanding & Exploration | Monthly trends: Banks live, UPI Volume & Value, combined plots | `DAY_2_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 3 | Data Cleaning & Feature Engineering | Rename columns, handle missing values, convert Month to datetime, extract Year, Month_Num, Quarter | `DAY_3_CAPSTONE_PROJECT_ipynb.ipynb` |
| 4 | Data Cleaning & Feature Engineering | Visualize cleaned dataset: Volume & Value growth, Banks live, Yearly aggregates | `DAY_4_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 5 | Trend Analysis & Fraud Prep | Calculate MoM & YoY growth, highlight anomalies, visualize trends | `DAY_5_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 6 | Trend Analysis & Fraud Prep | Correlation analysis, feature selection, encode categorical features, heatmaps | `DAY_6_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 7 | Predictive Modeling | Prepare dataset: label, train-test split, scale/normalize features | `DAY_7_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 8 | Predictive Modeling | Train models: Logistic Regression, Random Forest, XGBoost, compare performance | `DAY_8_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 9 | Predictive Modeling | Evaluate models: Confusion Matrix, ROC-AUC, F1-score, fine-tune hyperparameters | `DAY_9_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 10 | Predictive Modeling | Save best model, visualize predictions vs actual, document learnings | `DAY_10_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 11 | Dashboard | Build interactive dashboard with Streamlit/Dash: Volume & Value trends, Banks live, Yearly aggregates, optional model predictions | `DAY_11_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
| 12 | Deployment | Deploy dashboard online (Streamlit/Heroku), update README & GitHub repo, share portfolio link | `DAY_12_CAPSTONE_PROJECT.ipynb` |
